{"tid":2109693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★西貢1、2號專線小巴董事確診 平日會以乘客身份乘搭小巴","createTime":"2020-07-15T11:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T12:02:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"90f7dc0791fc6461175ed9298b8fbcc1ee7e1237","tid":2109693,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"近日新冠肺炎疫情反彈，本港今（15日）再新增19宗確診個案，今日網傳西貢專線小巴的老闆確診感染新冠肺炎，西貢1、2號專線小巴有限公司其後證實第1559號確診個案為其公司董事，但未有參與日常營運，平日會以乘客身份乘搭小巴。西貢區議員梁衍忻則指，目前小巴公司正在安排全線消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/498231/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%B0%88%E7%B7%9A%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B9%B3%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%98%E6%90%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%9A%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F498231%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E5%25B0%2588%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B9%2598%25E6%2590%25AD%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25AF%2592&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu4RM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=c60e82c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/498231/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%B0%88%E7%B7%9A%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%B9%B3%E6%97%A5%E4%B9%98%E6%90%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B4-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%9A%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92</a>"},{"pid":"9d961c17449c61854f23d6aaad3191d575af3878","tid":2109693,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class